{
  "id": "adv_event_2301_01_04",
  "title": "莉央不在のリズノワ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私達の一つ前のグループのステージ\n始まっちゃいましたよ。どうしましょう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh no‚ our previous group's stage has\nalready begun. What should we do…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.958276844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "落ち着いて、愛",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stay calm‚ Ai-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.1666666667,
      "endTime": 9.1713378112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "でも葵さん、リズノワの出番まで後二十分です\n……それまでに莉央さんが戻らなかったら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ Aoi-san‚ LizNoir's performance is just 20 minutes away.\n…If Rio-san doesn't return by then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3666666667,
      "endTime": 17.339342467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "……大丈夫\n莉央の責任感の強さは、君達も知ってるでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's going to be okay.\nYou all know how strong Rio-chan's sense of responsibility is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5666666667,
      "endTime": 23.0252832095,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央は絶対に戻って来る\nだから僕らは、平常心で準備を進めよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She will definitely come back.\nSo let's keep our cool and be prepared.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.2333333333,
      "endTime": 30.199999841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "乱れた心じゃ、いいパフォーマンスは出来ないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can't give a good performance if we lose control.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4,
      "endTime": 34.572040748599996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、ミキプロの人の陰謀でしょうか\n私達がバトルで負けるように……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could this be a conspiracy by the Miki guy?\nTo make us lose the battle…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7666666667,
      "endTime": 40.2699094455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "あんな男の罠に引っかかるほど莉央は間抜けじゃないよ\n……莉央からの返事はまだない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-chan isn't foolish enough to fall into the trap like that.\n…Still no response from Rio-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.4666666667,
      "endTime": 47.8500001589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、まだ既読も付かないですぅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nope‚ she hasn't even read the message…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.0666666667,
      "endTime": 53.0388435046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "センターの莉央さんがいないんじゃ\nステージなんて出来ませんよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If the center Rio-san isn't here‚\nwe can't perform…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2333333333,
      "endTime": 58.4925399144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "お願いです！　莉央さん、早く帰って来て下さい～っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please! Rio-san‚ come back soon!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7,
      "endTime": 63.572449207300004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "…………莉央",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…………Rio-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7666666667,
      "endTime": 65.5333333334,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2233.333333300003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "来たっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5333333333,
      "endTime": 67.77285714940001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5866.666666699999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "会場スタッフ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Venue",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "LizNoirさん、後十分です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir‚ you have 10 minutes left.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.1666666667,
      "endTime": 70.33333333329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "会場スタッフ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Venue",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そろそろ準備お願いしまーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need your preparations now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3333333333,
      "endTime": 72.5143308321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "あ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2666666667,
      "endTime": 75.48743766950001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "も、もしかしてこれ、リズノワ最大のピンチじゃ\nないでしょうか？　莉央さんがいないなんて初めてです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C-Could this be LizNoir's biggest crisis?\nWe never been wiithout Rio-san before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.7,
      "endTime": 84.5911560059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしましょう、葵さん……\n今更不参加なんて言えませんよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should we do‚ Aoi-san…?\nIt's too late to say we won't participate now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8,
      "endTime": 91.0956235886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "……当たり前だよ。僕らは星見プロを代表して\nこの合同ライブに参加してるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Of course not.\nWe're representing Hoshimi Prods. in this joint live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.3,
      "endTime": 98.889750576,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのみんなのメッセージを読んだでしょ？\nそれに、ファンが僕らを待ってる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You read the messages from Hoshimi Prods. members‚ right?\nBesides‚ the fans are waiting for us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.1,
      "endTime": 105.9854873657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "棄権なんて絶対にしない\n僕は一人でもステージに立つよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We won't withdraw.\nI'll perform alone if I have to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.2,
      "endTime": 111.71655321120001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私もご一緒します！\n葵さんを一人になんてしませんから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll join you!\nI won't leave Aoi-san alone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.9,
      "endTime": 116.39297075270001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こころだって、同じ気持ちです～\nどうせ死ぬなら、ステージの上で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too! I feel the same way!\nIf we're going down‚ it'll be on the stage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.6,
      "endTime": 123.38766422280001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2301_01_04-aoi011.m4a",
